   <title>Check that SVG in a foreign tags is not ignored</title>
   <body>
     <p>SVG works if you can see the uppercase version of "correct" after the colon:
       <foreign>
         <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            height="10">
           <text y="10" font-size="10">CORRECT</text>
         </svg>
       </foreign>
     </p>
   </body>
